{"tid":1809722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【11.2 港島衝突】20歲青年涉藏兩士巴拿　證據不足獲撤控兼贏訟費","createTime":"2020-01-03T09:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T10:42:38.000Z","uid":2748,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"80ebfde4614af11c71f603f1e3beb423268d8132","tid":1809722,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"2019年11月2日於港島區多處有人發起集會，20歲無業男子當日涉於銅鑼灣一帶攜有兩支士巴拿，早前被控1項管有適合作非法用途的工具罪。案件今（3日）於東區裁判法院再提訊，由於證據不足，控方申請撤銷控罪，但反對被告的訟費申請，指被告攜有自製盾牌、屬自招嫌疑。辯方反駁，控方所指的盾牌只是一個鐵盤；裁判官最終批准訟費申請。<br />\n<br />\n被告顏偉濠（20歲）早前被控1項管有適合作非法用途的工具罪。控罪指，被告於2019年11月2日，在銅鑼灣堅拿道西10號冠景樓外管有適合作非法用途的工具，即兩支士巴拿。<br />\n<br />\n控方今申請撤銷控罪，指現時證據未能符合定罪的最低要求，獲裁判官批准申請。<br />\n<br />\n辯方提出訟費申請，惟遭控方反對。控方指被告當日除了攜有兩支士巴拿外，更帶有頭盔及1面自製盾牌，而當日案發地點附近有示威衝突，形容被告當日自招嫌疑。<br />\n<br />\n辯方反駁，控方所指控的兩枝士巴拿只有手掌大小，而且厚度較薄，平常可以用作組裝模型，而控方所指的盾牌只是一個鐵盤，兩者都不是專用作犯罪的工具，裁判官最終批准被告的訟費申請。"},{"pid":"9ecf795da81e0b7408a5a93ce1cd952f74005ee1","tid":1809722,"uid":34869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"仆街真係屈得就屈"},{"pid":"940d08aa73fda39deaa9934e54589cb91dcf196d","tid":1809722,"uid":173326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"跟住班狗又上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bb240c51c04c69bbe6d128db12b21bc5d76d66","tid":1809722,"uid":108757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:01:01.000Z","msg":"裁判官係邊個，終於有個正常"},{"pid":"3a515998109e9675fa951e2b9f173b911386d8a3","tid":1809722,"uid":609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"手掌咁大既士巴拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你班黑警同律政司真係亂鳩咁告"},{"pid":"f23a95d2259bef07acfaba823be76be498633ca4","tid":1809722,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"鍵盤當盾牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁紙皮都可以當condom啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c6c003768a820b5045490a7b9996665b961b48","tid":1809722,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"72bb240c51c04c69bbe6d128db12b21bc5d76d66","tid":1809722,"uid":108757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:01:01.000Z","msg":"裁判官係邊個，終於有個正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:02:02.000Z","msg":"唔關事, 係控方撤控<br />\n唔關個官事<br />\n<br />\n可能唔撤的話個官照入"},{"pid":"18aa28cb6571a70207597d4407f135dc398df314","tid":1809722,"uid":170365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"940d08aa73fda39deaa9934e54589cb91dcf196d","tid":1809722,"uid":173326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"跟住班狗又上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"其實係啲濕鳩檢控官格硬嚟"},{"pid":"b50e3d067d952b675ee55e1c41b22f8079bdef2b","tid":1809722,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b682d64e6a586dff4fb7f2c2f7aaa93011cfd8","tid":1809722,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jwgr6vtGHgo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJwgr6vtGHgo&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7KjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=83567c6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jwgr6vtGHgo</a>"},{"pid":"bfff4eda8133fab399c8a669ab249636a343dfbf","tid":1809722,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"「自招嫌疑」算唔算現代莫須有"},{